name: Sky Jet X War
description:
Sky Jet X War is an air force strike & air battle game that will take you back to 1945 in the context of World War II. The real graphics of the air plane shooting games will make you feel like you are in a real aircraft war.
You can not miss a catchy and attractive fighting aircraft game like this one. All design is created with enthusiasm, you will not find anywhere plane games fighter like that.
features
- Sky high stunts simulator
- Flying jets with powerful weapons
- VFX effects with beautiful environment
